    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Seven of thirteen credibility factors assessed; all assessed factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping. The use-error factor is noted as not-assessed within this package, with a reference to a companion IEC 62366 human factors document; however, no linked evidence artefact is present. The assessment team accepted this gap on the basis that the IEC 62366 process is managed separately and that model influence is rated Medium (testing confirms results). Overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the COU decision at MRL 2.",
